title: Shipboard Propulsion, Power Electronics, and Ocean Energy
description:
English | ISBN: 1439888507 | 2012 | 289 pages | PDF | 10 MB 

Shipboard Propulsion, Power Electronics, and Ocean Energy fills the need for a comprehensive book that covers modern shipboard propulsion and the power electronics and ocean energy technologies that drive it. 

With a breadth and depth not found in other books, it examines the power electronics systems for ship propulsion and for extracting ocean energy, which are mirror images of each other.
